data.description: Don't wait to see this beautiful one story home in the heart of Central Florida!! Featuring an open floor plan, vaulted ceilings, and ample natural light throughout, this four bedroom, two bathroom home comes equipped with stunning accent walls in several rooms and a bonus room that leads to the backyard! With new flooring in the common areas, sleek granite countertops, and recently resurfaced kitchen cabinets, this house demonstrates a cozy, yet elevated elegance. This property is located just minutes from a myriad of shopping and entertainment venues including Disney Parks & attractions, Gatorland, Lego Land, and Universal Studios. This neighborhood is just two miles from the ramp to I-4, Florida's most traveled highway that can take you nearly anywhere in the state. The Forest is a community where individuals and families appreciate the pleasure of living in a vacation like environment, year round! This gorgeous home is nestled within one of Florida’s top gated, public golf course neighborhoods, and it's many lakes and greenery, add to the tropical ambiance and beauty of this tranquil paradise. Residents enjoy a large playground with picnic areas, tennis courts, and a heated community pool. The Forest at Ridgewood Lakes also features miles of biking and walking trails within it's gates! Advent Health’s Heart of Florida hospital is 3 miles away. On top of all that, the HOA fee for this gated community is only $100/month! Book your showing today because this GEM wont last long!    The Forest is one of five communities that together make up the Ridgewood Lakes. (Del Webb, High Vista, Ridgewood Pointe, The Forest, and The Gallery Condominium community)
